April 14 at 9:32 AM ·

DID YOU KNOW?...

If you have an iPhone or iPad you actually have a scanner! Parents, if you are planning to scan any work to your teachers or teachers if you are scanning work to your students you can use the ‘Notes App’.

Open a new note, press the camera button, the option to scan document will pop up. Once the document is scanned you can email it easier than a photo, plus you can add notes to the scanned doc. #themoreyouknow

post_text:
To my Seniors it's been a great ride. You all have been playing for me since Jr. High. It's not the outcome we expected as we went into spring break preparing for our district tournament. Little did we know our last tournament had just been played a few days before. Thank you for all the great memories, wish we could have made more before the year was over. I am thankful for the years you were with me. I know you all will have great success in the future. Class of 2020

Coach Briones

post_text:
Calling all current Juniors that are currently on track for the Health Science Pathway. If you are interested in applying for the Senior Practicum 2020-2021 class for certification in Patient Care Technician (PCT) and Certified Clinical Medical Assistant (CCMA), you need to submit an interest packet to Mrs. J. Perez no later than May 2, 2020. You can access the packet via the high school website.

Instruction to access the Interest packet for Senior Practicum:
1. Log onto the LFHS website (hs.laferiaisd.org)
2. Click on staff in the golden bar towards the top of the page
3. Enter in the search bar: JacLyn Perez
4. Click on the More (grey box)
5. Click on the My website with the globe
6. Click on Practicum Interest packet at the top of the page/black bar
There you will find all the contents of the packet along with the instructions for everything.

I am looking forward to the upcoming class of 2020-2021.

post_text:
Dear Parents/Guardians:

During this tying time, we know that our students are having to make may adjustments to their normal routine. Beginning Monday, March 30th, you can email your child's school counselor between the hours of 9:00 AM to 3:00 P.M. with any questions or concerns you or your child may have. Stay safe!

Sincerely, W.B. Green JH Counseling Department

Estimados Padres de Familia/Guardianes Legales:

En estos momentos de prueba que estámos viviendo, nuestros estudiantes han tenido que hacer muchos ajustes a su rutina normal. Comenzando el lunes 30 de marzo, usted puede comunicarse con la Consejera de su niño/a via correo eletrónico durante las horas de 9:00 am-3:00 p.m. con cualquier pregunta o preocupación que tenga acerca de su niño/a. Cuidense Mucho!

Departamento de Consejería de la Escuela W. B. Green JH
